{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "SHELF/quick_shapes", "parent": "create"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Quick Shapes"], "extent": [43, 60]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Creates different types of primitive geometry."], "extent": [60, 115]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [115, 129], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool creates primitive geometry in the Object (", {"type": "code", "text": ["/obj"]}, ") or Solaris (", {"type": "code", "text": ["/stage"]}, ") network. You can use it to create a box, tube, sphere, torus, or grid geometry. You can draw shapes onto the ground plane or off of existing visible geometry. You can turn on ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/ref/windows/snapoptions", "type": "link", "text": ["snapping"], "fullpath": "/ref/windows/snapoptions.html"}, " to snap the cursor when drawing shapes. This tool is useful when you're sketching out a scene."], "extent": [129, 519]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool behaves differently in LOPs. Instead of making separate LOP nodes, each shape is made inside of a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes//lop/sopcreate", "type": "link", "text": ["SOP Create LOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes//lop/sopcreate.html"}, ". The shapes are set up as well-structured USD primitives, and the transforms are accessible in Solaris."], "extent": [519, 769]}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [769, 775], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["This tool respects the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Default Context Creation"]}, " setting in the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/ref/windows/mainprefs#geo", "type": "link", "text": ["Objects and Geometry preferences"], "fullpath": "/ref/windows/mainprefs.html#geo", "fragment": "#geo"}, ". If you're drawing in SOPs, ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Create at Object Level"]}, " creates the shapes in the Object network and ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Create in Context"]}, " creates the shapes inside the current object."], "extent": [775, 1073]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"type": "task_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "task", "indent": 0, "text": ["Choose a shape"], "role": "item", "extent": [1073, 1095], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Press the number that corresponds to the shape you want to create."], "extent": [1095, 1166]}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"keys": ["1"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " Add a box."], "extent": [1166, 1189]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"keys": ["2"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " Add a tube."], "extent": [1189, 1213]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"keys": ["3"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " Add a sphere."], "extent": [1213, 1239]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"keys": ["4"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " Add a torus."], "extent": [1239, 1264]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"keys": ["5"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " Add a grid."], "extent": [1264, 1289]}], "container": true}], "container": true}, {"ext": null, "type": "task", "indent": 0, "text": ["Enter and exit Edit Mode"], "role": "item", "extent": [1289, 1321], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Press ", {"keys": ["H"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " to enter and exit Edit Mode."], "extent": [1321, 1367]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Use Edit Mode to select and move existing shapes that you haven\u2019t yet added as a node. Press ", {"keys": ["Delete"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " to remove any selected shapes."], "extent": [1367, 1507]}], "container": true}, {"ext": null, "type": "task", "indent": 0, "text": ["Switch to centered drawing"], "role": "item", "extent": [1507, 1541], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Hold ", {"keys": ["Shift"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " while drawing your shape. This draws the shape using the clicked point as the center of the shape instead of the corner."], "extent": [1541, 1682]}], "container": true}, {"ext": null, "type": "task", "indent": 0, "text": ["Switch to square drawing"], "role": "item", "extent": [1682, 1714], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Hold ", {"keys": ["Ctrl"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " or ", {"keys": ["Cmd"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " while drawing your shape. The shape is drawn as a cube."], "extent": [1714, 1800]}], "container": true}, {"ext": null, "type": "task", "indent": 0, "text": ["Exit the Quick Shapes tool"], "role": "item", "extent": [1800, 1834], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Press ", {"keys": ["Esc"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " to exit the Quick Shapes tool."], "extent": [1834, 1884]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using Quick Shapes"], "extent": [1884, 1909], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Smallicon", "value": "SHELF/quick_shapes", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SHELF/quick_shapes.html"}, " Quick Shapes button on the Create tab."], "extent": [1909, 1992]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Select the shape to create (see the preceding table)."], "extent": [1992, 2048]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Click and drag to draw the base of the shape."], "extent": [2048, 2096]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Move up and down to set the height of the shape. Click to select the height."], "extent": [2096, 2175], "body": [{"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 4, "role": "item", "extent": [2175, 2185], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["This step doesn\u2019t apply to a Grid shape."], "extent": [2185, 2234]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["For a tube shape, move up and down to set the top radius and make a cone. Click to select the radius."], "extent": [2234, 2338]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Do one of the following:"], "extent": [2338, 2365], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Draw another shape."], "extent": [2365, 2391]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " or exit out of the tool to add the shape as a node."], "extent": [2391, 2465]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Press ", {"keys": ["H"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " to enter Edit Mode (see the preceding table)."], "extent": [2465, 2529], "body": [{"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 8, "role": "item", "extent": [2529, 2543], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Once you add the shape as a node, you can\u2019t adjust it using the Quick Shapes\u2019s Edit Mode."], "extent": [2543, 2646]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true}]}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [2646, 2655], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/box", "type": "link", "text": ["Box"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/box.html"}], "extent": [2655, 2680]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/tube", "type": "link", "text": ["Tube"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/tube.html"}], "extent": [2680, 2707]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/sphere", "type": "link", "text": ["Sphere"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/sphere.html"}], "extent": [2707, 2738]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/torus", "type": "link", "text": ["Torus"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/torus.html"}], "extent": [2738, 2767]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/grid", "type": "link", "text": ["Grid"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/grid.html"}], "extent": [2767, 2794]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["Quick Shapes"], "summary": ["Creates different types of primitive geometry."]}